delete_rds_instance :

# Destroy RDS Database

Destroy an RDS database instance. As with EC2, before we can get rid of an
instance we have to disable termination protection.

    1.  Disable termination protection
        {
            click("Modify")
            navigate("bottom")
            deselect("Enable deletion protection")
            click("Continue")
            select("Apply Immediately")
            click("Modify DB instance")
        }
